{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"魔画\"中，王风与常笑在小楼中讨论血鹦鹉和僵尸的谜团。常笑对王风所见的血鹦鹉说话一事表示怀疑，认为鹦鹉通灵或需接受十万神魔传说。众人讨论万通的死因，发现他被七星绝命针毒杀后遭化尸散毁尸。唐老大提及江湖上使用化尸散的高手，包括陕北为虹子、河东乌鸦、河西赤雁和燕南毒手书生萧秋雨。王风透露铁恨曾侦破黑店，可能获得化尸散。常笑对这件奇案束手无策，已调查两年多。王风向常笑描述照壁上的魔画，描绘奇浓嘉嘉普诸魔聚会、血鹦鹉诞生的场景。血奴透露画是由郭繁的兄弟郭易所绘，王风因画中血奴神秘失踪而将其刷掉。常笑决定寻找僵尸踪迹，王风则表示害怕与常笑同行，因其\"毒剑常笑，活阎王\"的恶名。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"墓地上当时可有其他人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"一个也没有。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你不信那番话是出自血鹦鹉的口中？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那番话无疑应该是由人说的，但事实，是发自鸟口。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他摇摇头，又道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这时候僵尸应已出动了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你不怕？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他跟我是朋友。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"最好他变了僵尸之后，也仍认识你这个朋友。\"",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"认得与否是其次，只要见到他就成。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这仍不是我主要的目的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你主要的目的是什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"设法阻止他再变成僵尸。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你希望自己的朋友死后能够安息？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"很希望。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"交着你这种朋友实在不错。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你们已检查过万通的尸体？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"有什么发现？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哪几个？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他们跟铁恨可有关系？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"没有。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我记忆所及，大约在五六年前，铁恨在湘西曾经侦破一间黑店，在那间黑店后院，据讲是有一个化尸池，黑店的一伙谋财害命之后，就将尸体投入池中，毁尸灭迹……\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他霍地回头，盯着王风道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他一再摇头，叹息着道：\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"可是事实就存在，而且的确已发生。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我本来绝不信有所谓妖魔鬼怪，有所谓第二世界——\"",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你仍在怀疑？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你有没有见过僵尸杀人？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"连僵尸我都未见一面，又怎会见过僵尸杀人。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哦？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"等，我一定等，我还准备四出打寻他的踪迹。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你的胆子看来也不小。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"并不比你大，有你在一旁壮壮胆子最好。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"只可惜我现在仍然不想跟你混在一起。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你不是要去寻找铁恨的尸体？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我没有说过不去。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那我们何不走在一块儿，彼此也乐得有一个照应？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"也许你这是出自好意，但这种好意，我只能心领。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你是害怕我？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"害怕得要命。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"为什么？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"只因为你是毒剑常笑，活阎王常笑。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这种话我还是第一次听到。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"像我这种说话不顾后果的人，本来就很少。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"昨夜才刷过。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"谁刷的？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你是不是精力过剩，无处发泄。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我倦得连棺材都肯睡进去，你说是不是？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这面墙壁莫非有问题？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"大有问题，对着它，我就仿如置身奇浓嘉嘉普。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"奇浓嘉嘉普？\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"'奇浓嘉嘉普'就是诸魔聚会的地方，没有头上的天空，没有脚下的土地，只有风和雾，寒冰和火焰——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"墙上到底有什么？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"一幅画。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哪一天？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"诸魔齐贺魔王十万岁寿诞，滴血化鹦鹉的那一天。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"诸魔是什么样子？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"魔王又是什么样子？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那之外还有什么？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"十三只怪鸟，围绕血鹦鹉飞翔，有燕子的剪尾，有蜜蜂的毒针，半边的翅是蝙蝠，半边的翅是兀鹰，半边的羽毛是孔雀，半边的羽毛是凤凰——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他们也就是血鹦鹉的奴才。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"血奴？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"正是血奴。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我哪来这种本领。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他可有告诉你为什么他要这样做？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我从来没有听过那么奇怪的地方，于是就追问上去……\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你认为也是？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他那幅画画的好不好？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"好极了，他简直就是个画画天才。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"既然是这样，怎么你又肯让王风将那幅画刷掉？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"因为他也是一个魔王。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哦？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你又为什么要刷掉那幅画？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"因为那幅画有鬼。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哦\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你看着他飞出去？飞回来？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"如果我看到，现在我已在八百里外。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那你又怎知道那十三只血奴会飞去飞还？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"也许你开始就数错了？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"没有这种事。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你这么肯定？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你又听到它在什么地方冷笑？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"就在墙壁上。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"墙壁上还是墙壁里？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这也有分别？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"有，你可是不能肯定？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"墙壁后面是什么地方？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"另一个房间。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"谁住的？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"宋妈妈。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"并不算什么神圣，只是一个老巫婆。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"巫婆？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"因为她本来是血奴的奶妈，你是不是想跟她见上一面？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"很想。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你不妨着人去找她来。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我自己去找她？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你要到隔壁她所住的地方参观一下。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"一定要。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"门就在隔邻，最好找不过。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你不去？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我昨夜已去过一次，一次已足够。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你在那里看到了什么？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你可知一个脱光了的老太婆，是怎样的样子？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我虽然还没有这种机会，但亦可以想像得到。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"现在是你的机会了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你真的不去？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"是不是她爬到你身上？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"换转你，你怎样？逃不逃？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"逃得一定比你还快。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"所以，我认为你应该再去一次。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那种地方有什么好参观的？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"也许那个地方有些东西能够解开你心中的疑团。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"哦？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他姓郭。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"郭什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不知道。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "常笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他没有说过？\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他只说过有一个兄弟叫做郭繁，曾经亲眼见过血鹦鹉。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"原来是郭易。\"",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你怎知他是郭易？\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"郭繁根本就只有郭易一个兄弟。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    }
